1. Ti *ostaješ* ovde dok ja idem u prodavnicu. (You *stay* here while I go to the store.)
2. Ne znam zašto *ostaješ* tako dugo u kancelariji. (I don't know why you *stay* in the office for so long.)
3. Da li ćeš *ostati* sa mnom do kraja večeri? (Will you *stay* with me until the end of the evening?)
4. Oni *ostaju* u hotelu na obali mora. (They *stay* at a hotel on the seaside.)
5. Kada *ostaneš* sam, osetićeš se usamljeno. (When you are *left* alone, you will feel lonely.)
6. Ostavila sam ti poruku na stolu, ako *ostaneš* bez goriva nazovi me. (I left you a message on the table, if you *run out of* gas, call me.)
7. Nemoj da *ostaješ* budan celu noć, treba da se naspavaš. (Don't *stay* up all night, you need to get some sleep.)
8. *Ostajemo* bez vremena, moramo da se požurimo. (We are *running out of* time, we need to hurry.)
9. Kada *ostavim* posao, ne razmišljam o njemu do sledećeg radnog dana. (When I *finish* work, I don't think about it until the next workday.)
10. Ako *ostaneš* ovde, propustićeš svoj voz. (If you *stay* here, you will miss your train.)